---
title: Thai Spiced Fish Cakes with crunchy side salad and sweet chilli drizzle
description: If you're a fan of fish then you're going to adore these lightly spiced Thai fishcakes. Made with salmon and sweet potato, these fishcakes are fried to crispy perfection and bursting with flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R15_W17_IE_IECLF14140-3_Mainhigh-35149ffc.jpg
